0came%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20reports%20suggesting%20that%20the%20Indian%20side%20was%20working%20on%20an%20early%20meeting%20between%20the%20two%20leaders.%20President%20Trump%20and%20PM%20Modi%20enjoyed%20warm%20relations%20in%20the%20US%20president's%20first%20term%2C%20but%20during%20his%20campaign%20for%20re-election%2C%20the%2078-year-old%20American%20leader%20called%20India%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20big%20abuser%26quot%3B%20of%20trade%20and%20vowed%20to%20use%20tariffs%20on%20global%20imports%20into%20the%20US%20to%20correct%20imbalances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20threatened%20the%20BRICS%20group%20of%20nations%2C%20of%20which%20India%20is%20a%20part%2C%20with%20tariffs%20if%20they%20did%20not%20accept%20his%20demand%20of%20committing%20to%20not%20create%20a%20new%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Trade%20And%20Bilateral%20Relations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Monday's%20call%20with%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bemphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20India%20increasing%20its%20procurement%20of%20American-made%20security%20equipment%20and%20moving%20toward%20a%20fair%20bilateral%20trading%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20White%20House%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20India's%20largest%20trading%20partner%20and%20two-way%20trade%20surpassed%20%24118%20billion%20in%202023%2F24%2C%20with%20India%20posting%20a%20surplus%20of%20%2432%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20also%20an%20important%20strategic%20partner%20in%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20United%20States%20to%20counter%20China%2C%20and%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20on%20Monday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20called%20Mr%20Trump%20a%20%26quot%3Bdear%20friend%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20a%20mutually%20beneficial%20and%20trusted%20partnership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20work%20together%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20our%20people%20and%20towards%20global%20peace%2C%20prosperi