-deepseek-wakeup-call-ai-tech-giants-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20tech%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20spent%20on%20their%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20said%20its%20models%20were%20trained%20with%20fewer%20and%20less%20powerful%20semiconductor%20chips%20than%20their%20competitors%20typically%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202022%2C%20US%20sanctions%20have%20made%20it%20illegal%20for%20manufacturing%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fnvidia-tech-stocks-deepseek-ai-race-nasdaq-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20sell%20some%20of%20its%20chips%20to%20China%2C%20including%20its%20most%20advanced%20chips.%20The%20sanctions%20aimed%20to%20limit%20China's%20advancements%20in%20AI%20and%20military%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSanctions%20forced%20DeepSeek%20to%20use%20H800s%2C%20which%20were%20less%20powerful%20than%20H100s%2C%26quot%3B%20Patrick%20Moorhead%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Moor%20Insights%20and%20Strategy%2C%20told%20BI%20of%20the%20Nvidia%20chips%20DeepSeek%20has%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20roundabout%20way%2C%20sanctions%20initiated%20in%20the%20Biden%20administration%20motivated%20DeepSeek%20to%20be%20more%20creative%20in%20how%20it%20trained%20and%20ran%20models%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20should%20be%20surprised%2C%20as%20'necessity%20is%20the%20mother%20of%20invention.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d88c1190-9af2-4abb-9d78-b84e8d722ee5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMurky%20training%20and%20computing%20costs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20and%20analysts%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20expressed%20skepticism%20over%20DeepSeek's%20claims%20about%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20models%20and%20the%20number%20and%20type%20of%20chips%20they%20were%20built%20on.%20However%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20exactly%20what%20semiconductors%20were%20used%20to%20train%20and%20deploy%20DeepSeek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eanalysts%20said%20the%20startup%20showed%20that%20it's%20possible%20to%20do%20more%20with%20less%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeutsche%20Bank%20analysts%20Adrian%20Cox%20and%20Galina%20Pozdnyakova%20wrote%20of%20DeepSeek%20in%20a%20research%20note%20published%20Monday%3A%20%26quot%3BThey've%20had%20to%20squeeze%20more%20value%20out%20of%20their%20software%20and%20methods%20such%20as%20chain-of-thought%20reasoning%20and%20using%20several%20models%20at%20once%2C%20instead%20of%20just%20throwing%20more%20computing%20power%20at%20the%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Miller%2C%20author%20of%20the%202022%20book%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-tech-war-computer-chips-semiconductor-plants-costing-americans-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChip%20War%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20BI%20the%20DeepSeek%20models%20are%20impressive%20but%20that%20costs%20in%20AI%20have%20come%20down%20dramatically%20since%202023%2C%20so%20he%20did%20not%20find%20the%20company's%20latest%20paper%20especially%20surprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20the%20idea%20that%20DeepSeek%20was%20working%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bshoestring%20budget%26quot%3B%20was%20not%20true%2C%20saying%20the%20company%20used%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20narrow%20definition%20of%20training%20costs.%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20clear%20that%20the%20training%20cost%20is%20an%20order%20of%20magnitude%20higher%26quot%3B%20than%20DeepSeek%20suggested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d05ecee-6cb3-49cf-b4f4-135a37271990%5C%22%3EIneffective%20chip%20restrictions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlexandr%20Wang%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Scale%20AI%2C%20said%20during%20a%20January%2023%20CNBC%20interview%20that%20DeepSeek%20had%2050%2C000%20H800s%2C%20which%20Miller%20said%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%20number.%20%26quot%3B%20While%20that%20number%20is%20still%20much%20less%20than%20what%20US%20firms%20have%2C%20Miller%20said%2C%20it's%20likely%20a%20lot%20more%20than%20US%20export%20officials%20would've%20wanted%20a%20single%20Chinese%20firm%20to%20accumulate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZongyuan%20Zoe%20Liu%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20for%20China%20studies%20at%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20developments%20at%20DeepSeek%20suggest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-demo-chinese-ai-model-math-reasoning-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20development%20in%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bseems%20to%20be%20at%20least%20on%20par%20with%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20still%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20race%26quot%3B%20for%20AI%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20certainly%20serves%20as%20a%20good%20reminder%20for%20American%20policymakers%20that%20technology%20restriction%20may%20not%20work%2C%20depending%20upon%20what%20the%20end%20goal%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Liu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20experts%20said%20they%20thought%20the%20latest%20developments%20with%20DeepSeek%20could%20lead%20to%20even%20more%20semiconductor%20sanctions%20on%20China%20but%20would%20not%20necessarily%20stop%20further%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20could%20put%20sanctions%20on%20China%20all%20day%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Colello%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20there's%20always%20the%20threat%3A%20What%20if%20China%20comes%20up%20with%20some%20breakthrough%20anyway%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-deepseek-chip-restrictions-exports-imports-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738036613000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67983d74eb4be2fff9a25900%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-deepseek-chip-r