%3EMr%20Nadella%2C%20addressing%20the%20gathering%2C%20acknowledged%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20a%20product%20of%20the%20bond%20that%20exists%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20(India%20and%20US).%E2%80%9D%20He%20praised%20the%20leadership%20of%20both%20nations%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Cfocus%20on%20how%20to%20use%20technology%20to%20leverage%20education%20outcomes%2C%20health%20outcomes%2C%20public%20service%20efficiency%2C%20competitiveness%20and%20productivity%20of%20small%20businesses%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20press%20release%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20members%20of%20the%20Indian-American%20community%20at%20the%20Republic%20Day%20reception%2C%20Ferguson%2C%20the%20newly%20elected%2024th%20Governor%20of%20Washington%20State%2C%20acknowledged%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20incredible%20contribution%20the%20Indian%20society%20makes%20not%20just%20for%20India%20but%20for%20the%20entire%20world%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20as%20a%20new%20Governor%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Washington%2C%20he%20looked%20forward%20to%20building%20on%20the%20relationship%20with%20the%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Seattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20special%20recognition%20to%20mark%20the%20occasion%2C%20Washington%20State%20Senate%20in%20Olympia%20passed%20a%20State%20Senate%20Resolution%2C%20moved%20by%20State%20Senator%20Manka%20Dhingra%20and%20supported%20by%20Senator%20Vandana%20Slatter%2C%20welcoming%20the%2076th%20Republic%20Day%20of%20India%20and%20the%20strong%20friendship%20between%20the%20people%20of%20India%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Republic%20Day%20reception%2C%20hosted%20by%20the%20Consul%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Seattle%20Prakash%20Gupta%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20a%20distinguished%20line-up%20of%20top%20government%20officials%2C%20lawmakers%20as%20well%20as%C2%A0Mayors%20of%20ten%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20members%20of%20the%20US%20Congress%20who%20joined%20the%20evening%20celebrations%20included%20Rep.%