esident%20Donald%20Trump%20last%20week%20that%20changed%20the%20names%20of%20several%20American%20landmarks.%20Following%20the%20order%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20the%20Interior%20said%20the%20name%20changes%20were%20official%20and%20America's%20Geographic%20Names%20System%20was%20working%20%26quot%3Bexpeditiously%26quot%3B%20to%20fulfil%20the%20President's%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20longstanding%20practice%20of%20applying%20name%20changes%20when%20they%20have%20been%20updated%20in%20official%20government%20sources%2C%26quot%3B%20Google%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe've%20received%20a%20few%20questions%20about%20naming%20within%20Google%20Maps.%20We%20have%20a%20longstanding%20practice%20of%20applying%20name%20changes%20when%20they%20have%20been%20updated%20in%20official%20government%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20News%20from%20Google%20(%40NewsFromGoogle)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNewsFromGoogle%2Fstatus%2F1884012692048166951%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2027%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20name%20will%20reportedly%20be%20visible%20to%20Google%20Maps%20users%20in%20America%2C%20but%20the%20name%20will%20remain%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20Mexico%26quot%3B%20in%20Mexico.%20Outside%20of%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20users%20will%20see%20both%20names%20on%20Google%20Maps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Renaming%20Spree%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20Interior%20Department%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20has%20been%20officially%20changed%20to%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%2C%20and%20the%20Alaskan%20peak%20Denali%2C%20the%20tallest%20mountain%20in%20North%20America%2C%20has%20been%20renamed%20Mount%20McKinley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Maps%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20Alphabet's%20Google%2C%20will%20make%20a%20similar%20change%20with%20Mount%20McKinley.%20The%20Alaskan%20mountain%20was%20named%20Mount%20McKinley%20in%201917%20to%20honour%20America's%2025th%20president%2C%20William%20McKinley%2C%20However%2C%20it%20was%20renamed%20Denali%20during%20the%20Obama%20administration%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20ordered%20the%20name%20changes%20as%20part%20of%20a%20flurry%20of%20executive%20actions%20hours%20after%20taking%20office%20on%20January%2020%2C%20making%20good%20on%20a%20campaign%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20earlier%20this%20month%20jokingly%20suggested%20North%20America%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20be%20renamed%20%26quot%3BMexican%20America%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20historic%20name%20used%20on%20an%20early%20map%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle's%20Naming%20Policy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20applied%20the%20same%20locale-based%20labelling%20conventions%20to%20other%20locations%20subject%20to%20naming%20disputes.%20Outside%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea%2C%20the%20body%20of%20water%20bordering%20both%20nations%20is%20listed%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BSea%20of%20Japan%20(East%20Sea).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20Iran%20threatened%20to%20take%20legal%20action%20against%20Google%20over%20its%20decision%20to%20drop%20the%20term%20%26quot%3BPersian%20Gulf%26quot%3B%20from%20its%20Google%20Maps%20and%20leave%20the%20waterway%20between%20Iran%20and%20the%20Arabian%20peninsula%20nameless.%20The%20body%20of%20water%20is%20now%20labelled%20%26quot%3BPersian%20Gulf%20(Arabian%20Gulf)%26quot%3B%20in%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738032360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fbanj88fg_google-maps_625x300_18_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgoogle-maps-to-rename-gulf-of-mexico-t