%20the%20conversation%2C%20with%20Andreessen%20calling%20DeepSeek's%20model%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20amazing%20and%20impressive%20breakthroughs%26quot%3B%20he's%20ever%20seen.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20weekend%2C%20DeepSeek's%20AI%20assistant%20had%20rocketed%20to%20the%20top%20of%20Apple%20Inc.'s%20iPhone%20download%20charts%20and%20ranked%20among%20the%20top%20downloads%20on%20Google's%20Play%20Store%2C%20straining%20the%20startup's%20systems%20so%20much%20that%20the%20service%20went%20down%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour.%20The%20company%20was%20eventually%20forced%20to%20limit%20signups%20to%20those%20with%20mainland%20China%20telephone%20numbers%20-%20but%20claimed%20the%20move%20was%20the%20result%20of%20%26quot%3Blarge-scale%20malicious%20attacks%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fallout%20from%20the%20seemingly%20overnight%20surge%20in%20interest%20around%20DeepSeek%20was%20swift%2C%20and%20severe%3A%20The%20company's%20AI%20model%2C%20which%20it%20claims%20to%20have%20developed%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20rivals%20without%20meaningfully%20sacrificing%20performance%2C%20drove%20a%20nearly%20%241%20trillion%20rout%20in%20US%20and%20European%20technology%20stocks%20as%20investors%20questioned%20the%20spending%20plans%20of%20some%20of%20America's%20biggest%20companies.%20The%20share%20plunge%20in%20AI%20chipmaker%20Nvidia%20Corp.%20alone%20wiped%20out%20a%20record%20%24589%20billion%20in%20stock-market%20value%20from%20the%20world's%20largest%20company%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20stocks%2C%20including%20Nvidia%2C%20later%20erased%20some%20losses%20in%20after-hours%20trading.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20Monday%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20the%20overwhelming%20interest%20in%20DeepSeek's%20services%20was%20taking%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20company's%20system.%20%26quot%3BCurrently%2C%20only%20registration%20with%20a%20mainland%20China%20mobile%20phone%20number%20is%20supported%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20startup%20said%20on%20its%20status%20page.%20DeepSeek%20did%20not%20specify%20whether%20the%20signup%20curbs%20are%20temporary%20or%20how%20long%20they%20will%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20company's%20longest%20major%20outage%20since%20it%20started%20reporting%20its%20status.%20Unlike%20some%20rivals%2C%20DeepSeek's%20assistant%20shows%20its%20work%20and%20reasoning%20as%20it%20addresses%20a%20user's%20written%20query%20or%20prompt.%20Reviews%20on%20Apple's%20app%20store%20and%20on%20Alphabet%20Inc.'s%20Android%20Play%20Store%20praised%20that%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20quant%20fund%20chief%20Liang%20Wenfeng%2C%20DeepSeek's%20open-sourced%20AI%20model%20is%20spurring%20a%20rethink%20of%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20that%20companies%20have%20been%20spending%20to%20stay%20ahead%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20DeepSeek%20will%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20viable%2C%20cheaper%20alternative%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20initial%20worries%20are%20centered%20on%20whether%20US%20tech%20giants'%20pricing%20power%20is%20being%20threatened%20and%20if%20their%20massive%20AI%20spending%20needs%20re-evaluation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jun%20Rong%20Yeap%20of%20IG%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20all%20other%20Chinese-made%20AI%20models%2C%20DeepSeek%20self-censors%20on%20topics%20deemed%20politically%20sensitive%20in%20China.%20Unlike%20ChatGPT%2C%20DeepSeek%20deflects%20questions%20about%20Tiananmen%20Square%2C%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20or%20the%20possibility%20of%20China%20invading%20Taiwan.%20That%20may%20prove%20jarring%20to%20international%20users%2C%20who%20may%20not%20have%20come%20into%20direct%20contact%20with%20Chinese%20chatbots%20earlier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20success%20provides%20a%20counterpoint%20to%20expectations%20that%20the%20most%20advanced%20AI%20will%20require%20increasing%20amounts%20of%20computing%20power%20and%20energy%20--%20an%20assumption%20that%20has%20driven%20shares%20in%20Nvidia%20and%20its%20suppliers%20to%20all-time%20highs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20cost%20of%20development%20and%20energy%20consumption%20of%20DeepSeek%20are%20not%20fully%20documented%2C%20but%20the%20startup%20has%20presented%20figures%20that%20suggest%20its%20cost%20was%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20OpenAI's%20latest%20models.%20That%20a%20small%20and%20efficient%20AI%20model%20emerged%20from%20China%2C%20which%20has%20been%20subject%20to%20escalating%20US%20trade%20sanctions%20on%20advanced%20Nvidia%20chips%2C%20is%20also%20challenging%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20such%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20US%20is%20great%20at%20research%20and%20innovation%20and%20especially%20breakthrough%2C%20but%20China%20is%20better%20at%20engineering%2C%26quot%3B%20computer%20scientist%20Kai-Fu%20Lee%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20at%20the%20Asian%20Financial%20Forum%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20day%20and%20age%2C%20when%20you%20have%20limited%20compute%20power%20and%20money%2C%20you%20learn%20how%20to%20build%20things%20very%20efficiently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20its%20part%2C%20Nvidia%20-%20the%20biggest%20provider%20of%20chips%20used%20to%20train%20AI%20software%20-%20described%20DeepSeek's%20new%20model%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bexcellent%20AI%20advancement%26quot%3B%20that%20fully%20complies%20with%20the%20US%20government's%20restrictions%20on%20technology%20exports.%20The%20startup's%20work%20%26quot%3Billustrates%20how%20new%20models%20can%20be%20created%26quot%3B%20using%20a%20technique%20known%20as%20test%20time%20scaling%2C%20the%20company%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20statement%20appeared%20to%20dismiss%20some%20analysts'%20and%20experts'%20suspicions%20that%20the%20Chinese%20startup%20couldn't%20have%20made%20the%20breakthrough%20it%20has%20claimed.%20The%20company%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20inference%2C%20the%20work%20of%20actually%20running%20AI%20models%20and%20using%20it%20to%20process%20data%20and%20make%20predictions%2C%20nonetheless%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20its%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInference%20requires%20significant%20numbers%20of%20Nvidia%20GPUs%20and%20high-performance%20networking%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738030200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fnjniudc_deepseek-bloomberg_625x300_28_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-ai-startup-deepseek-hit-by-malicious-attacks-amid-sudden-fame-7575426%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Talk%20of%20an%20artificial-intelligence%20upstart%20in%20China%20behind%20a%20formidable%20ChatGPT%20rival%20had%20been%20building%20for%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-ai-startup-deepseek-hit-by-malicious-attacks-amid-sudden-fame-7575426%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Belarusian%20prez's%20'landslide'%20election%20win%20draws%20Putin's%20praise%2C%20West%20curbs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738030027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117615956%2Cimgsize-741294.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fbelarusian-prezs-landslide-election-win-draws-putins-praise-west-curbs%2Farticleshow%2F117615943.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117615943.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAlexander%20Lukashenko%20extended%20his%2031-year%20rule%20in%20Belarus%20after%20elec