nd%20open-source%20%E2%80%94%20excel%20at%20different%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20added.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20why%20the%20majority%20of%20Amazon%20Bedrock%20customers%20use%20multiple%20models%20to%20meet%20their%20unique%20needs%20and%20why%20we%20remain%20focused%20on%20providing%20our%20customers%20with%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20so%20they%20can%20easily%20experiment%20and%20integrate%20the%20best%20models%20for%20their%20specific%20needs%20into%20their%20applications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwitching%20costs%20for%20companies%20creating%20their%20own%20products%20on%20top%20of%20foundation%20models%20are%20relatively%20low%2C%20which%20is%20generating%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20as%20to%20whether%20DeepSeek%20will%20overtake%20other%20models%20from%20Meta%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20or%20OpenAI%20in%20popularity%20with%20enterprises.%20(It's%20already%20number%20one%20in%20Apple's%20app%20store.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%2C%20however%2C%20is%20owned%20by%20Chinese%20hedge%20fund%20High-Flyer%20and%20the%20same%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftik-tok-how-it-changed-everything-ban-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20concerns%20haunting%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20eventually%20apply%20to%20DeepSeek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20open-source%20models%20like%20DeepSeek%20present%20exciting%20opportunities%2C%20enterprises%E2%80%94especially%20in%20regulated%20industries%E2%80%94may%20hesitate%20to%20adopt%20Chinese-origin%20models%20due%20to%20concerns%20about%20training%20data%20transparency%2C%20privacy%2C%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Padval%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecurity%20concerns%20aside%2C%20the%20software%20companies%20that%20sell%20APIs%20to%20businesses%20have%20been%20adding%20DeepSeek%20throughout%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c5d6924-1bb7-4b84-842d-372cc745db70%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%204%3A%20Infrastructure%20players%20could%20take%20a%20hit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInfrastructure-as-a-service%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20Oracle%2C%20Digital%20Ocean%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20could%20be%20in%20a%20precarious%20position%20should%20more%20efficient%20AI%20models%20rule%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sheer%20efficiency%20of%20DeepSeek's%20pre%20and%20post%20training%20framework%20(if%20true)%20raises%20the%20question%20as%20to%20whether%20or%20not%20global%20hyperscalers%20and%20governments%2C%20that%20have%20and%20intend%20to%20continue%20to%20invest%20significant%20capex%20dollars%20into%20AI%20infrastructure%2C%20may%20pause%20to%20consider%20the%20innovative%20methodologies%20that%20have%20come%20to%20light%20with%20DeepSeek's%20research%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Stifel%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20same%20quantity%20of%20work%20requires%20less%20compute%2C%20those%20selling%20only%20compute%20could%20suffer%2C%20Barclays%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20increased%20uncertainty%2C%20we%20could%20see%20share%20price%20pressure%20amongst%20all%20three%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20and%20Digital%20Ocean%20declined%20to%20comment.%20Oracle%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20in%20time%20for%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d2536402-6bd3-470d-8770-05d4657919fe%5C%22%3ETake%205%3A%20Scaling%20isn't%20dead%2C%20it's%20just%20moved%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20months%2C%20AI%20luminaries%2C%20including%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20have%20been%20predicting%20a%20big%20shift%20in%20AI%20from%20a%20focus%20on%20training%20to%20a%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-players-startups-ai-inference-driving-prices-down-cheap-workload-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einference%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Training%20is%20the%20process%20by%20which%20models%20are%20created%20while%20inference%20is%20the%20type%20of%20computing%20that%20runs%20AI%20models%20and%20related%20tools%20such%20as%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20in%20computing's%20total%20share%20to%20inference%20has%20been%20underway%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20now%2C%20change%20is%20coming%20from%20two%20places.%20First%2C%20more%20AI%20users%20means%20more%20inference%20demand.%20The%20second%20is%20that%20part%20of%20DeepSeek's%20secret%20sauce%20is%20how%20improvement%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20inference%20stage.%20Nvidia%20took%20a%20positive%20spin%2C%20via%20a%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeepSeek%20is%20an%20excellent%20AI%20advancement%20and%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20Test%20Time%20Scaling.%20DeepSeek's%20work%20illustrates%20how%20new%20models%20can%20be%20created%20using%20that%20technique%2C%20leveraging%20widely-available%20models%20and%20compute%20that%20is%20fully%20export%20control%20compliant%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Nvidia%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInference%20requires%20significant%20numbers%20of%20NVIDIA%20GPUs%20and%20high-performance%20networking.%20We%20now%20have%20three%20scaling%20laws%3A%20pre-training%20and%20post-training%2C%20which%20continue%2C%20and%20new%20test-time%20scaling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225290c103-993e-4f60-995c-53bdef945537%5C%22%3ETake%206%3A%20Open-source%20changes%20model%20building%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20under-hyped%20part%20of%20DeepSeek's%20innovations%20is%20how%20easy%20it%20will%20now%20be%20to%20take%20any%20AI%20model%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20more%20powerful%20%26quot%3Breasoning%26quot%3B%20model%2C%20according%20to%20Jack%20Clark%2C%20an%20Anthropic%20cofounder%2C%20and%20a%20former%20OpenAI%20employee%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fimportai.substack.com%2Fp%2Fimport-ai-397-deepseek-means-ai-proliferation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%20about%20DeepSeek%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20newsletter%20Import%20AI%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClark%20also%20explained%20that%20some%20AI%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20OpenAI%2C%20have%20been%20hiding%20all%20the%20reasoning%20steps%20that%20their%20latest%20AI%20models%20take.%20DeepSeek's%20models%20show%20all%20these%20intermediate%20%26quot%3Bchains%20of%20thought%26quot%3B%20for%20anyone%20to%20see%20and%20use.%20This%20radically%20changes%20how%20AI%20models%20are%20controlled%2C%20Clark%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20providers%20like%20OpenAI%20had%20previously%20chosen%20to%20obscure%20the%20chains%20of%20thought%20of%20their%20models%2C%20making%20this%20harder%2C%26quot%3B%20Clark%20explained.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20now%20an%20open-weight%20model%20floating%20around%20the%20internet%20which%20you%20can%20use%20to%20bootstrap%20any%20other%20sufficiently%20powerful%20base%20model%20into%20being%20an%20AI%20reasoner.%20AI%20capabilities%20worldwide%20just%20took%20a%20one-way%20ratchet%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22adbb59ab-aac5-48c9-a4a4-a6d04a69d6fb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%207%3A%20Programmers%20still%20matter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20improved%20by%20using%20novel%20programming%20methods%2C%20which%20Samir%20Kumar%2C%20co-founder%20and%20general%20partner%20at%20VC%20firm%20Touring%20Capital%2C%20saw%20as%20a%20reminder%20that%20humans%20are%20still%20coding%20the%20most%20exciting%20innovations%20in%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%20that%20DeepSeek%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20good%20reminder%20of%20the%20talent%20and%20skillset%20of%20hardcore%20human%20low-level%20programmers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20tip%20or%20an%20insight%20to%20share%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EContact%20BI's%20senior%20reporter%20Emma%20Cosgrove%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20use%20the%20secure%20messaging%20app%20Signal%3A%20443-333-9088.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EContact%20Pranav%2