ggest%20it's%20a%20significant%20improvement%20over%20its%20third-quarter%20margin%20of%20-21%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%2C%20just%20overall%2C%20there's%20a%20stronger%20environment%20in%20the%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjetblue-founder-david-neeleman-budget-airlines-southwest-spirit-changes-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBreeze%20CEO%20David%20Neeleman%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20seen%20that%20from%20the%20earnings%20by%20other%20airlines%2C%20that%2C%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20they%20are%20doing%20better%20than%20they%20did%20last%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreeze's%20profitability%20comes%20as%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-end-of-budget-airlines-southwest-jetblue-frontier-spirit-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebudget%20rivals%20have%20failed%20to%20turn%20a%20full-year%20profit%20since%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%20halted%20travel%20and%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20the%20industry.%20That's%20a%20180-degree%20shift%20from%20before%2C%20when%20some%20low-cost%20airlines%20were%20growing%20faster%20than%20many%20mainline%20competitors.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20they%20face%20significant%20headwinds%20as%20travelers%20opt%20for%20more%20premium%20options%20offered%20by%20mainline%20carriers%20and%20grapple%20with%20continued%20high%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a658ff7b-da52-4652-aec5-4b6ac71eaf96%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENiche%20routes%20allow%20Breeze%20to%20avoid%20tough%20competition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENeeleman%2C%20known%20for%20launching%20five%20airlines%20including%20JetBlue%2C%20said%20Breeze%20is%20the%20sole%20operator%20on%20nearly%2090%25%20of%20its%20220%20nonstop%20routes.%20It%20avoids%20major%20airports%20to%20focus%20on%20underserved%20communities%2C%20such%20as%20Vero%20Beach%2C%20Florida%2C%20Mobile%2C%20Alabama%2C%20and%20New