e%20can%20get%2060%20or%2070%25%2C%20great%2C%20anything%20more%20than%2050%20it's%20a%20net%20positive%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Breeze%20Airways%20A220.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62a243354e21bf00185c2c0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBreeze's%20A220%20fleet%20offers%20five%20economy%20seats%20across.%20The%20first-class%20cabin%20is%202%C3%972.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpirit%20and%20Frontier%20have%20had%20to%20play%20catchup%20there%2C%20too.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMainline%20carriers'%20cheaper%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funited-basic-economy-review-carryon-middle-seat-new-york-denver-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebasic%20economy%20%3C%2Fa%3Efares%2C%20which%20often%20come%20with%20perks%20like%20a%20free%20carry-on%2C%20WiFi%2C%20drinks%20and%20snacks%2C%20and%20in-flight%20entertainment%2C%20have%20further%20poached%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBudget%20carriers%20have%20added%20some%20similar%20amenities%20to%20remain%20competitive%2C%20like%20adding%20new%20business-class-like%20seats%2C%20offering%20new%20bundling%20options%2C%20and%20waiving%20most%20change%20and%20cancel%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreeze-aiways-profit-ceo-interview-secret-weapon-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738015485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6797d69a7bb3f854015a7eb1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreeze-aiways-profit-ceo-interview-secret-weapon-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Breeze%20Airways%20is%20cashing%20in%20on%20premium%20revenue%20and%20its%20unique%20route%20structure%20while%20some%20budget%20competitors%20struggle%20to%20stay%20afloat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22trains%40insider.com%20(Taylor%20Rains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbreeze-aiways-profit-ceo-interview-secret-weapon-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20on-site%20natural%20gas%20plant%20will%20help%20power%20Stargate's%20first%20data%20center%2C%20public%20filings%20show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%2C%20Masayoshi%20Son%2C%20and%20Larry%20Ellison%20standing%20next%20to%20Sam%20Altman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67910cfbae09223df2baf5e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20SoftBank%20CEO%20Masayoshi%20Son%2C%20and%20Oracle%20founder%20Larry%20Ellison%20announced%20the%20Stargate%20project%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20January%2021.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDevelopers%20filed%20permits%20to%20operate%20natural%20gas%20turbines%20at%20Stargate's%20site%20in%20Abilene%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20turbines'%20combined%20capacity%20is%20360%20MW%2C%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20power%20Stargate's%20data%20centers%20need.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20electricity%20%E2%80%94%20enough%20to%20power%2090%2C000%20Texas%20homes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20developers%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-stargate-data-center-build-cost-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20Project%20Stargate%20data%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Abilene%2C%20Texas%2C%20plan%20to%20build%20a%20natural%20gas%20plant%20on%20the%20site%2C%20according%20to%20public%20filings%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20Oracle%2C%20and%20SoftBank%20have%20thus%20far%20provided%20little%20detail%20on%20the%20potential%20energy%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproject-stargate-ai-deepseek-donald-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStargate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-trump-stargate-build-agi-us-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoint%20venture%3C%2Fa%3E%20formed%20to%20spend%20%24500%20billion%20on%20AI%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20US%20and%20announced%20last%20week%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-ai-stargate-openai-oracle-softbank-technology-investment-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filings%20said%20that%20once%20operational%2C%20the%20plant%20could%20produce%20up%20to%20360.5%20megawatts%20of%20power%20at%20any%20given%20time%2C%20up%20to%2024%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%20365%20days%20a%20year.%20One%20MW%20of%20electricity%20can%20power%20250%20residential%20customers%20during%20peak%20hours%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ercot.com%2Ffiles%2Fdocs%2F2024%2F05%2F31%2FERCOT-Monthly-May-2024.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElectric%20Reliability%20Council%20of%20Texas%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%20This%20means%20360.5%20MW%20is%20enough%20to%20power%2090%2C000%20homes%20in%20Texas%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20double%20the%20amount%20of%20households%20in%20Abilene%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fquickfacts%2Ffact%2Ftable%2Fabilenecitytexas%2FPST120223%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Census%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20permit%20applications%20were%20filed%20with%20the%20Texas%20Commission%20on%20Environmental%20Quality%20by%20a%20consulting%20firm%20working%20on%20behalf%20of%20AI%20cloud%20startup%20Crusoe.%20Crusoe%20is%20the%20owner%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-stargate-data-center-build-cost-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProject%20Ludicrous%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%241.1%20billion%20data%20center%20project%20in%20Abilene%20widely%20thought%20to%20be%20the%20first%20Stargate%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20initial%20application%20to%20permit%2010%20simple-cycle%20natural%20gas%20turbines%20under%20Title%20V%20of%20the%20Clean%20Air%20Act%20%E2%80%94%20at%20a%20site%20that%20shares%20an%20address%20with%20Project%20Ludicrous%20%E2%80%94%20is%20under%20review%20by%20the%20TCEQ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20said%20the%20facility%20housing%20the%20turbines%20will%20be%20used%20for%20%26quot%3Bprimary%20and%20backup%20power%26quot%3B%20for%20%26quot%3Bdata%20centers%20and%20computing.%20%26quot%3B%20Its%20use%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bonsite%20only%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20the%20power%20generated%20by%20the%20turbines%20won't%20be%20available%20to%20the%20local%20grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20of%20the%20turbine%20models%20come%20from%20GE%20Vernova%2C%20and%20the%20other%20half%20come%20from%20Solar%20Turbines%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Caterpillar%20Inc.%20The%20turbines%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20installed%20and%20operational%20quickly%2C%20and%20some%20GE%20models%20can%20be%20up%20and%20running%20in%20as%20little%20as%20two%20weeks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gevernova.com%2Fgas-power%2Fproducts%2Fgas-turbines%2Flm250%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20company%20has%20said%20in%20marketing%20materials.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20permit%20allowing%20diesel-fired%20backup%20generators%20to%20run%20at%20the%20site%20is%20already%20in%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeveloping%20the%20plant%20is%20expected%20to%20cost%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars%2C%20a%20city%20document%20viewed%20by%20BI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Schmitt%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Crusoe%2C%20the%20startup%20developing%20Project%20Ludicrous%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20record%20about%20the%20natural%20gas%20plant.%20He%20directed%20BI%20to%20the%20company's%20previous%20comments%20about%20the%20site's%20power%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bincludes%20both%20on-and%20off-site%20renewable%20resources%2C%20including%20surrounding%20wind%20developments%20and%20a%20potential%20future%20large-scale%20onsite%20solar%20installation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20and%20Oracle%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2225ad2b74-d0ff-4f05-a1e4-f0105c8ee8f8%5C%22%3EStargate%20will%20need%20lots%20of%20power%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20analysts%20on%20Friday%20estimated%20the%20entire%20Stargate%20project%20would%20require%20about%2015%20gigawatts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20amount%20of%20power%20would%20be%20spread%20out%20across%20multiple%20locations%2C%20though%20the%20number%20of%20Stargate%20sites%20and%20how%20much%20power%20each%20would%20use%20is%20not%20publicly%20known.%20Some%20reports%20in%20the%20media%20and%20from%20financial%20analysts%20have%20indicated%20that%20Stargate%20sites%20could%20have%20a%20power%20demand%20of%205%20GW%2C%20an%20amount%20drawn%20from%20a%20document%20said%20to%20have%20been%20pitched%20by%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20to%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20first%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-09-24%2Fopenai-pitched-white-house-on-unprecedented-data-center-buildout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20then%20360.5%20MW%2C%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20natural%20gas%20turbines%20at%20Project%20Ludicrous%2C%20would%20make%20up%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20%E2%80%94%20less%20than%201%25%20%E2%80%94%20of%20how%20much%20power%20the%20site%20will%20ultimately%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20that%20power%20will%20come%20from%20a%20substation%2C%20allowing%20Project%20Ludicrous%20to%20draw%20power%20from%20the%20local%20electric%20grid.%20The%20data%20center%20is%20located%20on%20land%20owned%20by%20energy%20tech%20company%20Lancium%2C%20which%20has%20built%20a%20200%20MW%20substation%20on%20the%20site%2C%20a%20company%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20company's%20website%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20increase%20capacity%20to%20five%20times%20that%20amount%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20race%20to%20develop%20AI%20infrastructure%20has%20caused%20electricity%20demand%20in%20the%20US%20to%20soar%20dramatically%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20two%20decades.%20Data%20center%20electricity%20use%20could%20triple%20in%20the%20US%20by%202028%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feta-publications.lbl.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2024-12%2Flbnl-2024-united-states-data-center-energy-usage-report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20launch%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexplaining-deepseek-chinese-models-efficiency-scaring-markets-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepSeek%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20raised%20questions%20about%20AI%20infrastructure%20spending%20in%20the%20US%2C%20as%20the%20Chinese%20AI%20model%20is%2020%20to%2040%20times%20cheaper%20than%20OpenAI's%20and%20can%20run%20more%20efficiently%20with%20fewer%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20or%20have%20knowledge%20of%20the%20data%20center%20industry%20and%20have%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Get%20in%20touch%20with%20this%20reporter%20at%20ethomas%40insider.com%20or%20reach%20out%20via%20the%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20%2B1-929-524-6924.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstargate-data-center-powered-by-natural-gas-2025-1